high_descs: Go to the left, walk straight and turn right to go to the white table next to the door
Pick up the knife beside the bread and on top of the table
Walk back to the right to go to the counter top beside the green trash can
Slice the tomato beside the tea pot on the counter top using the knife.
Turn around and face the sink
Open the drawer underneath the blue plate, put the knife in and close the drawer.
Turn around and face the counter top again.
Pick up the slice of tomato from on top of the counter top.
Walk to the left and turn left to go to the microwave on the other side.
Open the microwave, put the slice of tomato in, heat it for a few seconds, pick it up again and close the microwave
Turn around to go to the green trash can nest to the counter top.
Put the slice of tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of heated tomato in the trash can.

high_descs: turn left and head to the door, then turn right and face the white table
pick up the knife from the table
turn right and head past the green recycling bin, then turn left and face the counter with the orange cup and red tomato on top
cut the red tomato into many slices
turn right, move forward slightly, then turn right and face the brown cabinets below the sink
open the brown drawer below the blue plate that's sitting on the counter, put the knife inside, then close the drawer
turn around and face the counter with the tomato on top
pick up a slice of the tomato
turn left and move forward to the door and stop just before the refrigerator, then turn left and face the red microwave

open the microwave, put the slice of tomato inside, then close the microwave, turn on the microwave and wait a bit, then turn the microwave off and open it, then pick up the tomato slice and close the microwave
turn around and move forward to the wall, then turn right and move forward to the green recycling bin
put the tomato slice in the green recycling bin
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of tomato into the green recycling bin.

Cut the tomato with the knife

Place the knife in the drawer
